EncounterParticipantFamilyNameSearchParameter

Parameter participant.family:string

Searches for Encounters based on the Practitioner's family name eg) /ws/fhir2/{release}/Encounter?participant.family={familyName}

ResourceEncounter
Expression(none)
Target ResourcesEncounter
MultiplesThe parameter cannot repeat or have multiple values
